Bouygues Offshore falls on weaker dollar . Shares in Bouygues Offshore , which rallied over the past month on the dollar ' s rise , fell heavily on Monday under the weight of a combination of a dollar slide and a fall on Wall Street , dealers said . At 0845 GMT , Bouygues Offshore was down 5 . 26 percent at 216 . 00 francs , following a rise to 232 francs on August 11 from 134 . 90 on June 24 . - - Paris newsroom + 33 1 4221 5452 
